'''克雷吉本山脈'''（Craigieburn Range）是[[新西兰|新西兰]][[南島_(新西蘭)|南岛]][[南阿爾卑斯山脈|南阿爾卑斯山脈]]的一部分。该山脉位于[[怀马卡里里河|怀马卡里里河]]南岸，{{link-en|亚瑟山口|Arthur's Pass}}以南，{{link-en|73号国道 (新西兰)|State Highway 73 (New Zealand)|73号国道}}以西。

在克雷吉本山脈從北到南有許多山峰，分別為<ref name=topomap>{{cite web |last=Harriss |first=Gavin |title=Topomap |url=http://www.topomap.co.nz/NZTopoMap/nz31532/CRAIGIEBURN%20RANGE/Canterbury |accessdate=6 April 2013 |archive-date=2021-01-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210130121416/http://www.topomap.co.nz/NZTopoMap/nz31532/CRAIGIEBURN%20RANGE/Canterbury |dead-url=no }}</ref>：       
* Baldy Hill{{Convert|1834|m}}
* 汉密尔顿峰（Hamilton Peak ）{{Convert|1922|m}}
* Nervous Knob{{Convert|1820|m}}
* 壁挂山（Mount Wall）{{Convert|1874|m}}
* 考山（Mount Cockayne）{{Convert|1874|m}}
* 芝士山（Mount Cheeseman）{{Convert|2031|m}}
* 奥林匹斯山（Mount Olympus）{{Convert|2094|m}}<ref name="Mt Olympus">{{Cite web|title=The Hill – Mt Olympus|url=http://www.mtolympus.co.nz/hill.asp|accessdate=6 April 2013|publisher=Windwhistle Winter Sports Club|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130813054224/http://mtolympus.co.nz/hill.asp|archivedate=2013-08-13|dead-url=no}}</ref>
* 伊扎德山（Mount Izard）{{Convert|2019|m}}以威廉·伊扎德（1851–1940）的名字命名
* 克劳斯利山（Mount Cloudesley）{{Convert|2107|m}}
* Mount Enys{{Convert|2194|m}}
* 卡恩·布雷亚（Carn Brea）{{Convert|2090|m}}
* 威利斯峰（Willis Peak）{{Convert|1962|m}}以Paul Hedley Willis（1941-2011 名字命名<ref name="Willis Peak">{{Cite web|title=Willis Peak officially named|url=https://www.linz.govt.nz/regulatory/place-names/place-name-consultation/14976|accessdate=3 February 2020|publisher=LINZ|archive-date=2020-02-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200203100716/https://www.linz.govt.nz/regulatory/place-names/place-name-consultation/14976|dead-url=no}}</ref>
* 蓝山（Blue Hill）{{Convert|1946|m}}

